name: Prime Office Products
overview: As of September 16, 2005, Prime Office Products, Inc. was acquired by Staples, Inc. Prime Office Products, Inc. supplies office products to local businesses. Its products include calendars, computer supplies, filing supplies, furniture, labels, mail and packing, money management, office equipment, office maintenance, papers and envelopes, pens and desk supplies, presentation products, and record keeping products. The company also involves in the wholesale and retail of office forms and supplies, office furniture, typewriters, and business machines. Prime Office Products was founded in 1999 as Business Essentials, Inc. and changed its name to Prime Office Products, Inc. in 2000. The company is based in Nashville, Tennessee.
